@startuml C4_Context
title System Context: YDB Qdrant-compatible Service

skinparam backgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #2563EB
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  FontColor #0F172A
}
skinparam database {
  BorderColor #4F46E5
  BackgroundColor #EEF2FF
  FontColor #0F172A
}

actor "IDE / RAG App\nRoo Code, Cline,\nor backend service" as user
rectangle "ydb-qdrant\n\nQdrant-compatible REST API\nNode.js library entrypoint\nExact top-k search\napi-key / userUid isolation" as ydbq
database "YDB\n\nqdr__collections\nqdrant_all_points\nqdrant_points_by_file" as ydb

user --> ydbq : Qdrant REST
ydbq --> ydb : YQL / SDK

note bottom of ydbq
  Public demo or self-hosted deployment.
  Supports million-vector collections when
  capacity and latency are sized for the workload.
end note
@enduml
